{"tid":2251721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有國泰員工稱空中服務員難轉行　但相信公司前景會好轉","createTime":"2020-10-21T03:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T04:18:02.000Z","uid":54800,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"71438cf3c87c3817c2fc67ccd7d1f1852746cee2","tid":2251721,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:50:25.000Z","msg":"國泰航空宣布，國泰航空集團包括國泰港龍航空將裁員8500人，任職國泰後勤部門兩年的[b]<span class=\"red\">林小姐說，現時未受裁員影響，但擔心將來有機會被裁減，她說自己很喜歡航空業，因此沒有找其他工作。</span><br />\n<br />\n林小姐表示，航空業的流動性低，空中服務員難轉行，不過相信公司前景會好轉，雖然航空業現在處於低迷，但未來仍然有需求。她又說，自己的工作與港龍航空相關，對於港龍停止營運感到可惜和不捨。"},{"pid":"ed4e20620d72a523765f07be8efefab2bb1bf722","tid":2251721,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:50:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1555873_1_L_20201021112508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1555873_1_L_20201021112508.jpg&h=32f53fde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />地勤都幾索~"},{"pid":"734140a87a223a47a4e4f070f5725d98ba9bd3e3","tid":2251721,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:56:03.000Z","msg":"收返套制服之後咁係難咗搵食嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e70aa7b78d0ac5ebfbe6675c01981b5c6e7a81","tid":2251721,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"林小姐明潤班同事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c714d5e590b750b6018864177475b623e94366d","tid":2251721,"uid":222336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"汰弱留強。俾咁多時間都唔搵定後路，怪得邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}